 <title>New Hope Bible Church in Lewiston, Maine - Sermons</title>
 <link>http://www.newhopebible.com/v2/taxonomy/term/5/0</link>
 <description>Sermons from New Hope Bible Church in Lewiston, Maine USA -- 
New Hope Bible Church is dedicated to helping people along their spiritual journey by addressing the tough questions of life with sober logic and scripture. We believe that Jesus Christ is the ultimate integration of all truths. We believe that only in Christ can we find unity and purpose for life.</description>
